Language Module

1.File structure
	Language
		|- fonts
		|	|- fontname1
		|	|	|- big
		|	|	|- small
		|	|	|- geobig
		|	|	|- geosmall
		|	|		|- unicode1.png
		|	|		|- unicode2.png
		|	|		|- .......
		|	|- fontname2
		|	|......
		|- lang1.dat
		|- lang1.yml
		|- .....
		|- langn.dat
		|- langn.yml

* fonts folder contains all supported fonts in form of folders. Folder name will
be used as font name.
* each font contains 4 subfolders including big, small, geobig and geosmall. 
